lead_paragraph: Alex Smith huddled with Chiefs offensive coordinator Matt Nagy in front of his locker, not more than 15 minutes after Kansas City had beaten the New Orleans Saints on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Alex Smith Leads Chiefs Past Mistake-Prone Saints, 27-21
